{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t17-train-3","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"代数式","title":"针对训练3：代数式求值综合","difficulty":4,"tags":["代数式","求值"],"content":"若 $|a + 1| + (b - 2)^2 = 0$，求 $3a^2 - 2ab + b$ 的值。","steps":[{"title":"求 a、b 的值","content":"由 $|a + 1| + (b - 2)^2 = 0$\n\n得 $a = -1$，$b = 2$","formula":"a = -1, b = 2"},{"title":"代入求值","content":"$3a^2 - 2ab + b$\n\n$= 3 \\times (-1)^2 - 2 \\times (-1) \\times 2 + 2$\n\n$= 3 + 4 + 2 = 9$","formula":"9"}]},"id":"t17-train-3"},"__N_SSG":true}